<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta
            name="viewport"
            content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
        />
        <title>칵테일 추천받기</title>
        <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.2.0/js/all.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="/staticComponent/header2.css"
        />
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="/staticComponent/footer.css"
        />
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="\surveyPage\surveyPage.css"
        />
    </head>
    <body>
        <div id="wrapper_ch">
            <header>
                <div id="header"></div>
            </header>
            <main>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q. 평소에 귀찮음을 자주 느끼 나요?</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q1"
                                id="Q1A1"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q1A1">1) 모든게 귀찮아요.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q1"
                                id="Q1A2"
                                value="6"
                            />
                            <label for="Q1A2"
                                >2) 할일을 겨우 끝내는 정도에요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q1"
                                id="Q1A3"
                                value="7"
                            />
                            <label for="Q1A3">3) 그냥 그래요.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q1"
                                id="Q1A4"
                                value="8"
                            />
                            <label for="Q1A4"
                                >4) 해야할 건 최선을 다해요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q1"
                                id="Q1A5"
                                value="9"
                            />
                            <label for="Q1A5">5) 무엇이든 열심히 해요.</label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q. 칵테일을 만들 때 재료가 다양하다면?</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q2"
                                id="Q2A1"
                                value="9"
                            />
                            <label for="Q2A1"
                                >1) 새로운 조합은 항상 기대되요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q2"
                                id="Q2A2"
                                value="8"
                            />
                            <label for="Q2A2"
                                >2) 단순한 칵테일은 맛이 지루한 것
                                같아요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q2"
                                id="Q2A3"
                                value="7"
                            />
                            <label for="Q2A3"
                                >3) 맛에 대한 의심과 기대가 동시에
                                생겨요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q2"
                                id="Q2A4"
                                value="6"
                            />
                            <label for="Q2A4"
                                >4) 오랫동안 고민하고 만들어 볼 것
                                같아요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q2"
                                id="Q2A5"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q2A5"
                                >5) 으악! 벌써 맛없을 것 같아요·</label
                            >
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q. 칵테일의 레시피가 너무 길다면?</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q3"
                                id="Q3A1"
                                value="4"
                            />
                            <label for="Q3A1"
                                >1) 만들기 전에 포기할 것 같아요</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q3"
                                id="Q3A2"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q3A2"
                                >2) 레시피를 대충 보고 만들어 먹을 것
                                같아요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q3"
                                id="Q3A3"
                                value="7"
                            />
                            <label for="Q3A3"
                                >3) 레시피가 뭐죠? 제맘대로 만들어 먹을
                                거에요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q3"
                                id="Q3A4"
                                value="9"
                            />
                            <label for="Q3A4"
                                >4) 레시피는 보라고 있는거에요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label
                                for="Q3A5"
                                style="visibility: hidden"
                                >>5)
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q. 평소에 단 걸 좋아하나요?</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q4"
                                id="Q4A1"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q4A1"
                                >1) 당뇨병에 걸릴 수도 있을 것 같아요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q4"
                                id="Q4A2"
                                value="4"
                            />
                            <label for="Q4A2"
                                >2) 항상 단 것이 먹고 싶어요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q4"
                                id="Q4A3"
                                value="3"
                            />
                            <label for="Q4A3"
                                >3) 있으면 먹지만 찾아먹진 않아요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q4"
                                id="Q4A4"
                                value="3"
                            />
                            <label for="Q4A4"
                                >4) 쓴 것을 싫어해서 먹는 정도에요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q4"
                                id="Q4A5"
                                value="2"
                            />
                            <label for="Q4A5">5) 사탕도 안좋아해요.</label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q. 칵테일을 마실 때 같이 먹고 싶은 음식은?</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q5"
                                id="Q5A1"
                                value="3"
                            />
                            <label for="Q5A1">1) 초콜릿 케이크</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q5"
                                id="Q5A2"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q5A2">2) 카나페</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q5"
                                id="Q5A3"
                                value="4"
                            />
                            <label for="Q5A3">3) 과일 안주</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q5"
                                id="Q5A4"
                                value="4"
                            />
                            <label for="Q5A4">4) 스테이크</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label
                                for="Q5A5"
                                style="visibility: hidden"
                                >5)
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q. 평소 시트러스(레몬, 라임)를 평소 좋아하나요?</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q6"
                                id="Q6A1"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q6A1">1) 완전 좋아해요.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q6"
                                id="Q6A2"
                                value="4"
                            />
                            <label for="Q6A2">2) 좋아해요.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q6"
                                id="Q6A3"
                                value="3"
                            />
                            <label for="Q6A3">3) 싫어해요.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q6"
                                id="Q6A4"
                                value="2"
                            />
                            <label for="Q6A4">4) 완전 싫어해요.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label
                                for="Q6A5"
                                style="visibility: hidden"
                                >5)
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q. 술 도수에 대해 어떻게 생각하시나요?</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q7"
                                id="Q7A1"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q7A1"
                                >1) 도수가 높아도 저에겐 "음료수"인걸요?</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q7"
                                id="Q7A2"
                                value="4"
                            />
                            <label for="Q7A2"
                                >2) 도수보다는 맛을 중요하게 생각해요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q7"
                                id="Q7A3"
                                value="3"
                            />
                            <label for="Q7A3"
                                >3) 내일을 걱정하는 숫자라고 생각해요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q7"
                                id="Q7A4"
                                value="2"
                            />
                            <label for="Q7A4"
                                >4) 도수가 낮으면 더 많이 마실 수 있어서 낮은
                                것이 좋아요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label
                                for="Q7A5"
                                style="visibility: hidden"
                                >5)
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q. 칵테일을 마시는 목적이 뭔가요?</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q8"
                                id="Q8A1"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q8A1">1) 오늘 맛있게 취할래요.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q8"
                                id="Q8A2"
                                value="4"
                            />
                            <label for="Q8A2"
                                >2) 잔잔한 분위기를 즐기고 싶어요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q8"
                                id="Q8A3"
                                value="3"
                            />
                            <label for="Q8A3"
                                >3) 데이트 때 마시기로 했어요.</label
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q8"
                                id="Q8A4"
                                value="2"
                            />
                            <label for="Q8A4">4) 간단하게 마시고 싶어요.</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label
                                for="Q8A5"
                                style="visibility: hidden"
                                >5)
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="surveyCard">
                    <h1>Q9</h1>
                    <form name="Qform">
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q9"
                                id="Q9A1"
                                value="5"
                            />
                            <label for="Q9A1">5</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q9"
                                id="Q9A2"
                                value="4"
                            />
                            <label for="Q9A2">4</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q9"
                                id="Q9A3"
                                value="3"
                            />
                            <label for="Q9A3">3</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input
                                type="radio"
                                name="Q9"
                                id="Q9A4"
                                value="2"
                            />
                            <label for="Q9A4`">2</label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label
                                for="Q9A5"
                                style="visibility: hidden"
                            >
                                5)
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="btn__container">
                    <button
                        type="button"
                        class="beforeQuestionBtn"
                    >
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-up"></i>
                    </button>
                    <button
                        type="button"
                        class="btn"
                    >
                        결과 보러 가기
                    </button>
                    <button
                        type="button"
                        class="afterQuestionBtn"
                    >
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-up"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
        <footer>
            <div id="footer"></div>
        </footer>
        <script src="./surveyPage/surveyPage.js"></script>
        <script src="/staticComponent/footer.js"></script>
        <script src="/staticComponent/header.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
